ygData.messageBody:
Hey the Rodcet Nife clan.. Fentus and geneasus ? i think thats it.. If there
is more let me know.. anyhow.. I am on vacation coming back on Monday Aug
30th to play. Anyhow, I will be power leveling that day ( to make up for
lost time) after that, I want to help you out a bit. We can work together
and get you some goodies or exp whatever you want pp?... So if you are for
it, please let me know. And what time works for you.. sometime on the
weekend ? Preferablly where you have some extra time.. I really want to
adventure with ya and have a good time.

So all Rodcet Nife peoples , email me and let me know when and where.. (oh
yeah, I seem to stick around the freeport oasis area.. ) Most of my
adventures are around that area or stem from that area
